    dc:description "FIGURES 139–146. Lomechusoides wellenii Palm, 1949. 139, male paralectotype, dorsal habitus; 140, pronotum in dorsal view (L: 1.15 mm, W: 1.85 mm), (locality: Svecia, Svartbyn); 141, male, aedeagus, lateral view; 142, male, aedeagus, ventral view; 143, male, metaventral process; 144, apex of paramere; 145, female, spermatheca, (locality: Svecia, Sangis); 146, female, spermatheca, (locality: Fennia Nyl., Helsinge). Scale bars in mm." ;
